        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3993365520" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7731851301828188067">Did you know Louisa May Alcott wrote a Gothic romance thriller? Well, you should. This manuscript was not published in her lifetime. It is one of her earliest works and attempts at getting her writing into print. You feel the suspense and dread with each turning page as Rosamond is stalked by her obsessive ex, each moment of safety so fleeting. <br/><br/>Favorite quotes: &quot;...at twenty the heart is wonderfully gifted with the power of outliving trials which later would break it at once or burden it for lif</span>
  <span id="freeText7731851301828188067" style="display:none">Did you know Louisa May Alcott wrote a Gothic romance thriller? Well, you should. This manuscript was not published in her lifetime. It is one of her earliest works and attempts at getting her writing into print. You feel the suspense and dread with each turning page as Rosamond is stalked by her obsessive ex, each moment of safety so fleeting. <br /><br />Favorite quotes: "...at twenty the heart is wonderfully gifted with the power of outliving trials which later would break it at once or burden it for life."<br /><br />"He was the first, the only love of her life, and in a nature like hers such passions take deep root and die hard." </span>
  <a data-text-id="7731851301828188067" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
