<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/51165909-beauty-mark"><img alt="Beauty Mark: A Verse Novel of Marilyn Monroe" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1582083090l/51165909._SX98_.jpg" />
